        everything you need to nurture and support your little one as they grow.
      </p>
      <div class="read_bt_1"><a href="#">Read More</a></div>
    </div>

    <div class="vegetables_section layout_padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="image_2">
          <img src="myImages/shop.png" style="height: 75px" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="about_taital">Our Store</h1>
        <p class="lorem_text">
          Welcome to <strong>BabyCare</strong>, your go-to destination for
          high-quality baby essentials from trusted brands. We offer a seamless
          shopping experience with our
          <strong>easy-to-navigate platform</strong> and
          <strong>fast nationwide delivery</strong> across Bangladesh. Join the
          <strong>BabyCare family</strong> for expert advice, premium products
          and exceptional service designed to make your parenting journey easier
          and more fulfilling!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="vegetables_section_2 layout_padding">
        <div class="row" style="padding: 0 15px">
          <% products.forEach(product => { %>
          <!-- <div class="col"> -->
          <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
            <div class="box_section">
              <div class="image_4" style="height: 300px">
                <img src="<%= product.image_path %>" />
              </div>
              <h2 class="dolor_text" style="padding: 10px 0">
                <%= product.product_price %> TK
              </h2>
              <a href="/product/<%= product.id %>"
